{"tid":94500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「有圖」坐火車就臭死","createTime":"2017-01-25T09:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T10:38:13.000Z","uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df280b71eda86cfd8e54b7c2f83816eba8d49d81","tid":94500,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"一上火車頭等見到得一個位<br />\n就沖過去坐<br />\n點知睇真d<br />\n對面原來有個bb<br />\n已經感覺不安<br />\n一坐低個bb就突然大聲叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘈到死<br />\n點知叫叫下突然收聲<br />\n變左喊<br />\n佢老母突然幫佢除褲<br />\n露左粒米出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再180度轉佢個身<br />\n之後就惡夢開始<br />\n見到佢老母開始搞佢屎忽<br />\n用紙狂抹佢屎忽<br />\n抹幾十分鐘都仲有<br />\n懷疑佢屙爛屎<br />\n臭到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g88YEwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg88YEwZ.jpg&h=d8b581de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無巴絲打教下小弟如何無視bb屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1d610267e77588713517831deb1007e7f6ea46","tid":94500,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"俾錢入去聞屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bca4e6f232af53165d90a466a9e25e5b7b72a66","tid":94500,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"搭火車預左嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069f6f7b634e452bd75da50f3249aeb6f2cdb138","tid":94500,"uid":79306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fc0938a8db10e96c2492bc9bc3491d