ets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係你親眼睇到都唔撚會信"},{"pid":"c2a2caf81ca12a2d951b7d3ac0bcc73f80e2ca09","tid":94500,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐得頭等都遇到咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇佢地似大陸人多，<br />\n叫人查佢飛分分鐘佢地無俾到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年我咁大個仔第一次坐都遇到類像既事，<br />\n兩條大陸佬係到傾計，講到鬼咁大聲，<br />\n就連我塞埋耳塞都聽到佢地d鬼話，<br />\ncall 到職員黎，職員居然話如果覺得受到影響，就自己去第2個車箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後狗鐵職員仲護送埋佢地出關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係你親眼睇到都唔撚會信</blockquote><br />\n直接行過去屌柒兩隻支那狗啦<br />\n有時間既咪同佢地慢慢嘈囉<br />\n咪撚旨意狗鐵D職員啦"},{"pid":"a0379d37ab45e58f70273f7a8675198bd08a1df3","tid":94500,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"個兩個支那人狂唱支那歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb070e03b8f1ac3f6c80cf5c71c4ccc0ea9c6f2","tid":94500,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐得頭等都遇到咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇佢地似大陸人多，<br />\n叫人查佢飛分分鐘佢地無俾到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年我咁大個仔第一次坐都遇到類像既事，<br />\n兩條大陸佬係到傾計，講到鬼咁大聲，<br />\n就連我塞埋耳塞都聽到佢地d鬼話，<br />\ncall 到職員黎，職員居然話如果覺得受到影響，就自己去第2個車箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後狗鐵職員仲護送埋佢地出關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係你親眼睇到都唔撚會信</blockquote><br />\n直接行過去屌柒兩隻支那狗啦<br />\n有時間既咪同佢地慢慢嘈囉<br />\n咪撚旨意狗鐵D職員啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就係屌到人叫職員個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n職員黎到個兩條大陸黎仲嘈緊，想黎打我，<br />\n我朋友叫我唔好再出聲，<br />\n話職員會解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時聽左佢講，所以咁既結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個有坐係附近既港豬同我講佢地坐頭等無俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗 你無撚遲d 再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次遇到咁既事真係唔怕玩大佢，<br />\n對依d 人真係零容忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2151985bbcb45cf617af62dec754d1cdce61f914","tid":94500,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"用口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好似食屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea96efc005ab5033e3c0f511eeb8484489eb5881","tid":94500,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"頭等唔郁佢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcfb9ff8d1228883797bd6526cd5c98fb6f6446","tid":94500,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好似食屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過用口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f800d240731ce379f43189dae405efe4e589249","tid":94500,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好似食屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過用口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/f